<li>Computerworld <a href="http://www.computerworld.com/softwaretopics/software/appdev/story/0,10801,65532,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.computerworld.com/softwaretopics/software/appdev/story/0,10801,65532,00.html" rel="nofollow">article</a> on clean room design</li>
